                    <decoNote type = "frame" xml:id = "d01">
                    Decorative designs: <locus target = "#1r #26v"/><foreign xml:lang = "gez">ሐረግ፡</foreign> using black and red, usually with eyes);
                    <locus target = "#iv(erso)"/>(<foreign xml:lang = "gez">ሐረግ፡</foreign> using black);
                    <locus target = "#29r #30v #31v #33r #34v"/> (dotted line using alternating black and red);
