                        with incipit <foreign xml:lang = "gez">እግዚእየ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወወልደ፡ ማርያም፡ ሥግው፡ በእንተ፡ ማርያም፡ ርድዓኒ፡...በእንተ፡ ወላዲትከ፡ ተሣሃለኒ፡ ወተዘክረኒ፡...</foreign>
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a2">
                        <locus target = "#9v"/>
                        <desc type = "Asmat">
                        Asmat prayer against the enemy, writeen backward
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a3">
                        <locus target = "#10r"/>
                        <desc>
                        The first stanza (of five lines) from the hymn, "Wise of the Wise," <title ref = "LIT2393tabiba"/>, as a prayer of salvation.
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a4">
